<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7189] Allow DIH to extract content from embedded documents via Tika</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7189</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;DIH&apos;s TikaEntityProcessor doesn&apos;t currently extract content from embedded documents/attachments within a file.  It might be useful if users could configure whether or not to include extraction of content from embedded documents.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
